 Preferred cost refers to the most common budget range chosen by users for a route;
 Preferred frequency refers to the most common travel frequency chosen by users for a route (e.g., daily, weekly).

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS recent_updates_count
FROM route_updates
WHERE update_date >= DATE('now', '-7 days');

external_knowledge:
